details.name: Haunt
details.description: Creates a spectral nemesis to attack each enemy hero after a short delay. At any moment during the duration, Spectre can use Reality to exchange places of a given haunt. Haunt illusions are uncontrollable, take extra damage, and deal less damage than Spectre herself.  They move at 400 base movement speed and ignore terrain. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.
details.upgrade_description: Grants you a new ability, Shadow Step. Allows you to perform a single target unit Haunt
